title: Don't buy any fire bolt watch, very low quality building
'Easy to Use. Great Quality within Cheap Price.'
body: 'I am using it for health and fitness check and to keep a track of it.  Black is my favourite color and black colored smart watch is a treat to my eyes.  A nice quality watch in a cheap price.  Definitely easy to use.  I just wish there were few more features in it and also few more interesting games.  Its great help to be able directly make and receive calls from the smrtwatch.  Once charged..it does work for enough time.  The watch design is really good. I loved it. I especially loved the option to adjust the belt size acoording to us on our own. The sound quality is great. And its water proof which is an advantage. Not to mention the availability of games. Overall its a good experience. Definiyely Loving it....!!!'
